      "actionDesc": "Introduced in House",
      "text": "<p><strong>Hydropower Relicensing Transparency Act</strong></p><p>This bill directs the Federal Energy Regulatory Commission to report annually to Congress on the status of the&nbsp;relicensing process for each application for a renewed hydropower dam license.</p>",
